Docs.value: An int bit map representing supported types.

remarks.para: Gets supported interactive app types.
The supported interactive app types is in a bit map format. For example:
remarks.code: int types = tvInteractiveAppInfo.getSupportedTypes(); if (types & TvInteractiveAppInfo.INTERACTIVE_APP_TYPE_HBBTV != 0) { // HbbTV type is supported. Do something... } if (types & TvInteractiveAppInfo.INTERACTIVE_APP_TYPE_ATSC == 0) { // ATSC type is not supported. Do something... }
